[Cite as 05/17/2002 Case Announcements, 2002-Ohio-2345.]

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

May 17, 2002

DISCIPLINARY CASES

1998-0783 and 1998-1793. Disciplinary Counsel v. Brown.

IT IS ORDERED by this court, sua sponte, that Thomas C. Brown, Attorney Registration No. 0024054, last known business in Geneva, Ohio, is found in contempt for failure to comply with this court’s order of November 7, 2000, to wit, failure to surrender his certificate of admission and attorney registration card and failure to file an affidavit of compliance on or before December 7, 2000.
